{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-0",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 02 传统机器学习分类器\n",
    "\n",
    "> 北京交通大学《机器学习与Python编程》研究性专题 — 裂纹图像识别系统\n",
    "\n",
    "本 Notebook 包含：\n",
    "1. 特征提取流水线（HOG + LBP + GLCM + 边缘密度）\n",
    "2. 三种传统分类器训练（决策树、SVM、KNN）\n",
    "3. 分类器性能对比与评估\n",
    "4. 混淆矩阵与 ROC 曲线可视化"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-1",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import sys\n",
    "import time\n",
    "from pathlib import Path\n",
    "\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "from tqdm.auto import tqdm\n",
    "\n",
    "# 添加项目根目录到 sys.path\n",
    "PROJECT_ROOT = Path.cwd().parent\n",
    "if str(PROJECT_ROOT) not in sys.path:\n",
    "    sys.path.insert(0, str(PROJECT_ROOT))\n",
    "\n",
    "from src.config import DATA_ROOT\n",
    "from src.data_utils import load_dataset, split_dataset\n",
    "from src.models.traditional import (\n",
    "    DecisionTreeClassifier,\n",
    "    KNNClassifier,\n",
    "    SVMClassifier,\n",
    "    TraditionalClassifier,\n",
    "    compare_classifiers,\n",
    "    extract_features,\n",
    ")\n",
    "from src.evaluation.metrics import compute_metrics, plot_confusion_matrix, plot_roc_curve\n",
    "from src.plot_config import set_chinese_font\n",
    "\n",
    "set_chinese_font()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-2",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. 数据加载与特征提取\n",
    "\n",
    "加载完整数据集，将每张图像提取为 HOG + LBP + GLCM + 边缘密度的组合特征向量。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-3",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 加载完整数据集\n",
    "print("正在加载完整数据集，请稍候...")\n",
    "t0 = time.time()\n",
    "images, labels = load_dataset(DATA_ROOT)\n",
    "elapsed = time.time() - t0\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f"数据集总量：{len(images)} 张")\n",
    "print(f"正样本（有裂纹）：{np.sum(labels == 1)} 张")\n",
    "print(f"负样本（无裂纹）：{np.sum(labels == 0)} 张")\n",
    "print(f"加载耗时：{elapsed:.1f} 秒")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-4",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 使用全量数据：70% 训练 / 15% 验证 / 15% 测试\n",
    "X_train_img, X_val_img, X_test_img, y_train, y_val, y_test = split_dataset(\n",
    "    images, labels, train_ratio=0.7, val_ratio=0.15, random_seed=42\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f"训练集: {len(y_train)} 张 (正: {np.sum(y_train==1)}, 负: {np.sum(y_train==0)})")\n",
    "print(f"验证集: {len(y_val)} 张 (正: {np.sum(y_val==1)}, 负: {np.sum(y_val==0)})")\n",
    "print(f"测试集: {len(y_test)} 张 (正: {np.sum(y_test==1)}, 负: {np.sum(y_test==0)})")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-5",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 1.1 批量特征提取\n",
    "\n",
    "对每张图像调用 `extract_features()` 提取组合特征向量：\n",
    "- **HOG**（~1764 维）：方向梯度直方图，捕获裂缝方向性\n",
    "- **LBP**（59 维）：局部二值模式直方图，捕获纹理模式\n",
    "- **GLCM**（48 维 = 3 距离 × 4 角度 × 4 属性）：灰度共生矩阵纹理统计\n",
    "- **边缘密度**（1 维）：Canny 边缘像素占比\n",
    "\n",
    "> 特征提取对每张图片耗时约 0.1–0.2 秒，全量数据预计需要若干分钟。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-6",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def batch_extract_features(image_list, desc="提取特征"):\n",
    "    \"\"\"批量提取特征，返回 (N, D) 的 numpy 数组。\"\"\"\n",
    "    features = []\n",
    "    for img in tqdm(image_list, desc=desc):\n",
    "        features.append(extract_features(img))\n",
    "    return np.stack(features)\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "print("正在提取训练集特征...")\n",
    "t0 = time.time()\n",
    "X_train = batch_extract_features(X_train_img, desc=\"训练集特征提取\")\n",
    "print(f"训练集特征矩阵：{X_train.shape}，耗时 {time.time() - t0:.1f} 秒")\n",
    "\n",
    "print("\\n正在提取验证集特征...")\n",
    "t0 = time.time()\n",
    "X_val = batch_extract_features(X_val_img, desc=\"验证集特征提取\")\n",
    "print(f"验证集特征矩阵：{X_val.shape}，耗时 {time.time() - t0:.1f} 秒")\n",
    "\n",
    "print("\\n正在提取测试集特征...")\n",
    "t0 = time.time()\n",
    "X_test = batch_extract_features(X_test_img, desc=\"测试集特征提取\")\n",
    "print(f"测试集特征矩阵：{X_test.shape}，耗时 {time.time() - t0:.1f} 秒")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f"\\n特征维度总结：{X_train.shape[1]} 维")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-7",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. 分类器单模型训练与评估\n",
    "\n",
    "分别训练决策树、SVM、KNN 三种分类器，在测试集上评估性能。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-8",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 2.1 决策树"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-9",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 训练决策树\n",
    "dt = TraditionalClassifier(model_type="decision_tree", random_state=42)\n",
    "t0 = time.time()\n",
    "dt.fit(X_train, y_train)\n",
    "dt_train_time = time.time() - t0\n",
    "print(f"决策树训练耗时：{dt_train_time:.2f} 秒")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 预测\n",
    "y_pred_dt = dt.predict(X_test)\n",
    "y_prob_dt = dt.predict_proba(X_test)[:, 1]\n",
    "\n",
    "# 评估\n",
    "dt_metrics = compute_metrics(y_test, y_pred_dt, y_prob_dt)\n",
    "print(f"\\n决策树测试集结果：\")\n",
    "for k, v in dt_metrics.items():\n",
    "    print(f\"  {k}: {v:.4f}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-10",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 决策树混淆矩阵与 ROC 曲线\n",
    "fig_cm_dt = plot_confusion_matrix(y_test, y_pred_dt)\n",
    "plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "fig_roc_dt = plot_roc_curve(y_test, y_prob_dt, label="决策树")\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-11",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 2.2 SVM（支持向量机）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-12",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 训练 SVM（RBF 核，含 StandardScaler 预处理）\n",
    "svm = TraditionalClassifier(model_type="svm", kernel="rbf", probability=True, random_state=42)\n",
    "t0 = time.time()\n",
    "svm.fit(X_train, y_train)\n",
    "svm_train_time = time.time() - t0\n",
    "print(f"SVM 训练耗时：{svm_train_time:.2f} 秒")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 预测\n",
    "y_pred_svm = svm.predict(X_test)\n",
    "y_prob_svm = svm.predict_proba(X_test)[:, 1]\n",
    "\n",
    "# 评估\n",
    "svm_metrics = compute_metrics(y_test, y_pred_svm, y_prob_svm)\n",
    "print(f"\\nSVM 测试集结果：\")\n",
    "for k, v in svm_metrics.items():\n",
    "    print(f"  {k}: {v:.4f}")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-13",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# SVM 混淆矩阵与 ROC 曲线\n",
    "fig_cm_svm = plot_confusion_matrix(y_test, y_pred_svm)\n",
    "plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "fig_roc_svm = plot_roc_curve(y_test, y_prob_svm, label="SVM")\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-14",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 2.3 KNN（K 近邻）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-15",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 训练 KNN\n",
    "knn = TraditionalClassifier(model_type="knn", n_neighbors=5)\n",
    "t0 = time.time()\n",
    "knn.fit(X_train, y_train)\n",
    "knn_train_time = time.time() - t0\n",
    "print(f"KNN 训练耗时：{knn_train_time:.2f} 秒")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 预测\n",
    "y_pred_knn = knn.predict(X_test)\n",
    "y_prob_knn = knn.predict_proba(X_test)[:, 1]\n",
    "\n",
    "# 评估\n",
    "knn_metrics = compute_metrics(y_test, y_pred_knn, y_prob_knn)\n",
    "print(f"\\nKNN 测试集结果：\")\n",
    "for k, v in knn_metrics.items():\n",
    "    print(f"  {k}: {v:.4f}")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-16",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# KNN 混淆矩阵与 ROC 曲线\n",
    "fig_cm_knn = plot_confusion_matrix(y_test, y_pred_knn)\n",
    "plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "fig_roc_knn = plot_roc_curve(y_test, y_prob_knn, label="KNN")\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-17",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. 三种分类器综合对比"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-18",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 汇总所有指标\n",
    "results = {\n",
    "    "决策树": dt_metrics,\n",
    "    "SVM": svm_metrics,\n",
    "    "KNN": knn_metrics,\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "# 训练耗时\n",
    "train_times = {\n",
    "    "决策树": dt_train_time,\n",
    "    "SVM": svm_train_time,\n",
    "    "KNN": knn_train_time,\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "# 表格展示\n",
    "df_results = pd.DataFrame(results).T\n",
    "df_results["训练耗时(s)"] = pd.Series(train_times)\n",
    "df_results.index.name = "分类器"\n",
    "print(df_results.round(4).to_string())"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-19",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 指标柱状图对比\n",
    "metrics_names = ["accuracy", "precision", "recall", "f1"]\n",
    "metric_labels = ["准确率", "精确率", "召回率", "F1 分数"]\n",
    "classifier_names = list(results.keys())\n",
    "\n",
    "fig, axes = plt.subplots(1, 4, figsize=(18, 4))\n",
    "colors = ["#4e79a7", "#f28e2b", "#59a14f"]\n",
    "\n",
    "for i, (metric, label) in enumerate(zip(metrics_names, metric_labels)):\n",
    "    values = [results[c][metric] for c in classifier_names]\n",
    "    bars = axes[i].bar(classifier_names, values, color=colors)\n",
    "    axes[i].set_title(label)\n",
    "    axes[i].set_ylim(0, 1.05)\n",
    "    axes[i].set_ylabel(label)\n",
    "    # 在柱上标注数值\n",
    "    for bar, val in zip(bars, values):\n",
    "        axes[i].text(\n",
    "            bar.get_x() + bar.get_width() / 2,\n",
    "            bar.get_height() + 0.01,\n",
    "            f"{val:.4f}",\n",
    "            ha="center",\n",
    "            va="bottom",\n",
    "            fontsize=9,\n",
    "        )\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.suptitle("传统分类器性能对比", fontsize=14, fontweight="bold")\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-20",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# ROC 曲线合并对比\n",
    "from sklearn.metrics import roc_curve, roc_auc_score\n",
    "\n",
    "fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(8, 6))\n",
    "\n",
    "pred_data = [\n",
    "    ("决策树", y_prob_dt, "#4e79a7"),\n",
    "    ("SVM", y_prob_svm, "#f28e2b"),\n",
    "    ("KNN", y_prob_knn, "#59a14f"),\n",
    "]\n",
    "\n",
    "for name, y_prob, color in pred_data:\n",
    "    fpr, tpr, _ = roc_curve(y_test, y_prob)\n",
    "    auc = roc_auc_score(y_test, y_prob)\n",
    "    ax.plot(fpr, tpr, color=color, linewidth=2, label=f"{name} (AUC = {auc:.4f})")\n",
    "\n",
    "ax.plot([0, 1], [0, 1], color="gray", linestyle="--", alpha=0.5, label="随机猜测")\n",
    "ax.set_xlabel("假阳性率 (FPR)")\n",
    "ax.set_ylabel("真阳性率 (TPR)")\n",
    "ax.set_title("ROC 曲线对比")\n",
    "ax.legend(loc="lower right")\n",
    "ax.grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-21",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 训练耗时对比\n",
    "fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(6, 4))\n",
    "bars = ax.bar(train_times.keys(), train_times.values(), color=["#4e79a7", "#f28e2b", "#59a14f"])\n",
    "ax.set_ylabel("训练时间 (秒)")\n",
    "ax.set_title("三种分类器训练耗时对比")\n",
    "for bar, val in zip(bars, train_times.values()):\n",
    "    ax.text(\n",
    "        bar.get_x() + bar.get_width() / 2,\n",
    "        bar.get_height() + max(train_times.values()) * 0.01,\n",
    "        f"{val:.2f}s",\n",
    "        ha="center",\n",
    "        va="bottom",\n",
    "        fontsize=10,\n",
    "        fontweight="bold",\n",
    "    )\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-22",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. 使用统一接口对比\n",
    "\n",
    "调用 `compare_classifiers()` 函数，使用内置默认参数进行统一对比（验证结果与手动训练一致）。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-23",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 调用统一的 compare_classifiers 函数\n",
    "compare_results = compare_classifiers(X_train, y_train, X_test, y_test)\n",
    "\n",
    "df_compare = pd.DataFrame(compare_results).T\n",
    "df_compare.index.name = "分类器"\n",
    "print(df_compare.round(4).to_string())\n",
    "\n",
    "# 可视化\n",
    "df_compare.plot(kind="bar", figsize=(10, 5), rot=0)\n",
    "plt.title("compare_classifiers() 统一对比结果")\n",
    "plt.ylabel("分数")\n",
